'''國際陰陽人組織中文版'''是[[雙性人|雙性人]]的倡导和支持小组，也是国际阴阳人组织的中文分支机构。該組織是由[[丘愛芝|丘愛芝]]于2008年创立，活跃于台湾，香港和东亚其他地区。<ref name="times">{{cite web | url = http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/feat/archives/2013/11/27/2003577754/ | title = Neither here, nor there | work = [[Taipei_Times|Taipei Times]] | date = November 27, 2013 | accessdate = 2020-07-23 | archive-date = 2017-04-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170430094023/http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/feat/archives/2013/11/27/2003577754 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

== 任务与活动 ==
该组织的目标是结束[[雙性人|雙性人]]儿童的「正常化」手术，提高对[[雙性人|雙性人]]问题的认识，并提高政府对性别的认识。[[丘愛芝|丘愛芝]]表示，外科手术「正常化」做法始于1953年的台湾。作为这项任务的一部分，[[丘愛芝|丘愛芝]]于2010年在台北的LGBT骄傲游行中发起了「全球擁抱陰陽人」运动。该组织还發起演讲和游说政府。<ref name="times" /><ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.lihpao.com/?action-viewnews-itemid-136232 | title = 擁抱陰陽人 系列2：停止矯正手術 陰陽兒不是異形 | work = Lihpao Daily | date = 23 December 2013 | accessdate = 2020-07-23 | archive-date = 2015-07-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150703234800/http://www.lihpao.com/?action-viewnews-itemid-136232 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.gaystarnews.com/article/taiwan-allows-legal-gender-changes-without-transitioning091213 | title = Taiwan to allow legal gender changes without transitioning | work = [[Gay_Star_News|Gay Star News]] | date = 9 December 2013 | accessdate = 2020-07-23 | archive-date = 2016-05-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160526045841/http://www.gaystarnews.com/article/taiwan-allows-legal-gender-changes-without-transitioning091213/ | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.libertytimes.com.tw/2013/new/nov/3/today-o2.htm | title = Germany recognises gender 'X' | work = [[Liberty_Times|Liberty Times]] | date = November 3, 2013 | accessdate = 2020-07-23 | archive-date = 2013-11-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131107024126/http://www.libertytimes.com.tw/2013/new/nov/3/today-o2.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://blog.rti.org.tw/english/2011/01/20/intersex-hiker-chius-story/ | title = Intersex: Hiker Chiu’s story | work = [[Radio_Taiwan_International|Radio Taiwan International]] | date = January 20, 2011 | access-date = January 8, 2014 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161222160528/http://blog.rti.org.tw/english/2011/01/20/intersex-hiker-chius-story/ | archive-date = 2016-12-22 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>

== 隶属关系 ==
